Sec. 3. The name of a person whose name is required to be
redacted under this chapter must be replaced with a descriptive
anonymous designator, such as "Child Witness No. 1" or
"Passenger". Initials or references to familial relationships may
not be used.
Sec. 4. If a reference to an unredacted name or other
